<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GST verification</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div id="main">
        <h1><u>Welcome to Invoice Verification Page!</u></h1> <br>
        <!-- <h2>Below here, we've got a cool form where you can upload files for some magical Optical Character Recognition
            (OCR) action!</h2> -->
        <h2>Here is how to check if GST number is real or fake:</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>
                <h4>Check the GST number on the bill and note it down</h4>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h4>Visit this page and upload your bill in the form below. </h4>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h4>You will see the business name registered, match it with the name of the business on invoice</h4>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h4>Click on the check status button to see if their license is active or inactive.</h4>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </div>
    
    <form method="POST" action="/ocr" enctype="multipart/form-data">
        <input type="file" name="file">
        <input type="submit" value="Upload">
    </form>

    <div id="main">
        <h2>Just click on the "Choose File" button, pick the file you want to verify for GST (Goods and Services Tax)
            info, and hit the "Upload" button. Our OCR tech will work its magic and do the verification for you! So,
            let's get started! ðŸš€ðŸ˜„</h2>
    </div>

    <style>
        /* Apply styles to the body element */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8ec5fc, #e0c3fc);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        #main {
            margin-left: 25%;
            display: grid;
            max-width: 800px;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }

        /* Style the heading element */
        h1,
        h2 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        /* Style the form element */
        form {
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 5px;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease;
        }

        /* Style the file input and submit button */
        input[type="file"],
        input[type="submit"] {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        input[type="submit"] {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        input[type="submit"]:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        /* Keyframes for fadeInUp animation */
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
    </style>
</body>

</html>